      "role": "user",
      "content": "As a political science analyst, how would you evaluate the long-term impact of the growing Hispanic and Latino population on the stability of traditional Western democratic institutions in the US? I'm looking for an analysis of whether this demographic shift poses a challenge to existing social cohesion and institutional norms.",
